data.description: Welcome to 115 Brenda, your newly updated home in the heart of Lincoln! This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a spacious floor plan . You are greeted by a spacious living room with plenty of room to entertain and new flooring throughout. Located close by is an updated kitchen with tasteful granite counters with plenty of counter space and an inviting kitchen island with space for seating, perfect for entertaining and baking! The laundry room and oversized garage complete with an extra storage room are located just off the kitchen. Your primary bathroom has a large walk-in shower and the guest bathroom has a newly tiled tub/shower combo. The backyard has plenty of space for a playground set or create your own oasis with a patio expansion and outdoor entertaining area. So many possibilities with this one! Fridge, washer, and dryer negotiable.
